00:21:13,721 --> 00:21:16,988
-Karakura red-- Jinta Hanakari!

574
00:21:17,021 --> 00:21:18,321
-I said I'm red!

575
00:21:18,354 --> 00:21:19,321
Do you hear me?

576
00:21:19,354 --> 00:21:20,288
-Shut up already!

577
00:21:20,321 --> 00:21:21,288
I'm red!

578
00:21:21,321 --> 00:21:22,888
-Well you're not fit to be red!

579
00:21:22,921 --> 00:21:24,221
-You're more like yellow!

580
00:21:24,254 --> 00:21:26,821
-And Karakura gold, the leader
producer of the Karakura

581
00:21:26,854 --> 00:21:29,388
Superheroes, is the charismatic,
highly-rated television

582
00:21:29,421 --> 00:21:32,121
personality and natural
born hero Don Kanonji!

583
00:21:32,154 --> 00:21:33,054
-Leader?

584
00:21:33,088 --> 00:21:34,521
-What do you mean,
Karakura gold?

585
00:21:34,554 --> 00:21:35,454
That's a bunch crap!

586
00:21:35,488 --> 00:21:36,921
-Tune in every one!

587
00:21:36,954 --> 00:21:38,588
It's time you put
aside your differences

588
00:21:38,621 --> 00:21:40,388
